{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574110/extras/LyingSouls_Steam_Chair_GIF.gif?t=1724981444\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">THE GAMEPLAY</h2>In Lying Souls, you experience a story in which you have to solve the mysterious circumstances of a long-ago incident in your family in first person. You will experience different parts of the story to piece together the truth.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">THE STORY</h2>It's been a while since the incident. Back then you were too young to understand. Now you start looking for clues and realize that there is a cruel secret behind it all, and haunted by the consequences of the incident, you do your best not to lose your mind.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574110/extras/LyingSouls_Steam_Redstack_GIF.gif?t=1724981444\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">MAIN FEATURES</h2><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Story / Decisions:</li></ul></strong> You will have to make a decision at some moment. There are smaller and bigger decisions. But whether you will find out everything, is questionable.<br><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Notes / Recordings:</li></ul></strong> You will come across a number of audio recordings and various writings and notes. They will help you put the story together.<br><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Random Events:</li></ul></strong> You will experience some random events from time to time. They are always part of the current story and gameplay when they happen.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574110/extras/LyingSouls_Steam_Fire_GIF.gif?t=1724981444\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Happy Birthday!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1574110/0fc4ce111b4690bd923b64e6e2a678325ee42f3f.jpg"},{"name":"This is Art!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommun